original_title: Super Simple Songs - Here We Go Looby Loo
overview: Sing and dance to this Super Simple and fun version of the classic nursery rhyme "Here We Go Looby Loo"! This collection of kids songs and nursery rhymes also includes Open Shut Them 2, This Is The Way We Get Dressed, Are You Hungry? and more fun and educational songs for kids!
